ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:20:20.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有關黑警黨鐵破壞<br />\n<br />\n我有個大膽嘅想法 求吓你哋入嚟 幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639929</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebad849ecbd4c4fe99caed0fa3feacb46040fe5e","tid":1639773,"uid":70493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:49:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我相信正常人係唔會走去果度跳海<br />\n咁係被殺推落海嘅機會已經大得多"},{"pid":"1f66c65c5220a3809ce3c957d9cff0a5fde4e93b","tid":1639773,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"6723a4a625a91c0bb0b8c786d56ad4be755cf2d7","tid":1639773,"uid":264141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/09/111415_7dd1806cb6f01b3dd53cf2e6e5bca057.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F09%2F111415_7dd1806cb6f01b3dd53cf2e6e5bca057.png&h=1cfb68d6&s={SIZE}\" />）<br />\n<br />\n假設<br />\n第一點 17:00係消防員到達時間<br />\n第二點 估計消防員接到案件再到達現場需要15分鐘<br />\n所以大約第一個報案嘅時間為16:45分<br />\n按以上兌換表的話第一個報警嘅地點距離185米至463米！<br />\n（希望有人提供確實報案時間，目擊地點)"},{"pid":"96eb329b414083ef0f3f257d2b804a7f10d7cde7","tid":1639773,"uid":264141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KK51VVQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKK51VVQ.png&h=3546b6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHWHFnA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHWHFnA.png&h=b08ce6cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdFxh9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdFxh9i.png&h=85b07606&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SP3ffV1.png\" data-thumbn